* 1C Weak Strong

- (13)--15 balanced / semi-balanced (5-4-2-2), 5--3--3--2 maybe 5 card !h/!s
- 16+ unbalanced
- 21+ balanced

** 1C--1D

- Negative 0--7 hcp or flat 8--9 hcp semi-positive no 4cM
- Semi-positive is very limited ~8--9 hcp, less than an unconditional invite
- Many semi-positive 9 hcp flat hands are worth an invite
- Possibly pass with minimum weak NT and very concentrated values in a 5!ds hand
- Bid spades first, always canapé, bid longer !ss (natural) AND shorter !ss (canapé) first with 1!s
- Every other suit bid in longest suit natural order
- Extra strength showing bids - 1!h and 2!s/3!c/3!d are longest suit natural ordered

