** 1C--1HS

- 8+ hcp
- 4+ card suit
- Minor canapé
- Bid 1!h with 4--4 both majors
- Bid 1!s with 5--5 both majors
- No major canapé (bid longest major first)
- Unbalanced if GF (maybe balanced 4 card major if not GF)
- After a positive major response there is *no canapé bidding from opener* responders 1HS
  is already canapé and only one side of the partnership ever does canapé bidding.

